    tmp = 0.11
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.exp((tmp + 0.27 / v0 + 0.68)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.40 * v0 + 0.87) + (v2 + 0.63 * v1 + 0.51)) - wp.sin(0.20))
